adm1dae : Python package license and attribution notice

Package:
    adm1dae

Recommended install command:
    pip install adm1dae

Public API:
    from adm1dae import simulate

Compiled modules provided in the wheel:
    adm1dae.adm1_DAE2_bsm2
    adm1dae.pHsolv_bsm2
    adm1dae.Sh2solv_adm1

Packaged and maintained by:
    Dr Taher Abunama (tabunama@gmail.com)

Acknowledgements:
    The adm1dae package was prepared by Dr Taher Abunama based on the original ADM1 / BSM2 implementation and related algebraic solver components developed by the upstream academic authors.

Request:
    Please send feedback and, if you use this package in research/publications, acknowledge both the upstream ADM1 implementation authors and this Python packaging work.